                                operators `||' (``or''), `&&'
                                (``and'') and `!' (``not'').
* Conditional Exp::             Conditional expressions select between two
                                subexpressions under control of a third
                                subexpression.
* Function Calls::              A function call is an expression.
* Precedence::                  How various operators nest.


